    # ... rest unchanged
```

**Frontend changes:**
- Update all URLs that link to auction details and place bid pages to use auction_id, e.g., `/auction/1` instead of `/auction/vintage-leather-watch`.

This fix ensures URL parameters are consistent with the frontend element IDs and avoids issues with spaces or case sensitivity in item names, making the website operable and compliant with the regulations.
